{"type": "article", "id": 27175, "title": "京都这间办公室相当不错，它脱胎于传统日本民居", "description": "墙面的颜色非常耐看。\r\n", "date": "2016-05-23T06:54:54Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 501, "name": "办公室"}, {"id": 22971, "name": "京都"}, {"id": 7, "name": "艺术"}, {"id": 27969, "name": "Case-Real"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 179, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016070318030097s8dNWgUmnPpoCr.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>          </p>\n<p>对艺术工作者来说，办公室是一个微妙的环境，它需要激发创造力，有时候也具有向客人展示自己风格的需求。</p>\n<p>这对在京都 gosho-higashi 的夫妇分别从事着食品设计和策展的工作，对日本传统手工艺很有兴趣。他们交给建筑事务所 Case-Real 的房子是一种日本传统的仓库 <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kura_(storehouse)\">Kura (storehouse)</a>，试图把它改建成一个像家一样的办公室，“我们想要创造一个有多种用途的空间，功能分明却又相互影响”。</p>\n<p>这种仓库通常用木材和石头搭建，拥有特殊的防火性能。它沿着街道和相邻的建筑呈现半包围的格局，中间留有一个方形的花园，非常传统。在十字路口转角处的建筑是两层的，夹在两个入口的中间，这一部分改建成日常生活和会客的地方，拥有客厅、餐厅、厨房、卫生间和客房等房间，就像一个小的住宅。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031802523n7xQcuqlJfRwYzH.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70740741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>          </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">右侧是整体平面图，左半部分是入口处的放大</p></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031802525DGpkiLFdyZqwOE4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031802533qd019C7vUMBSJXV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>另一排建筑则是集中的工作室，面朝花园排列，相互之间用推拉门相隔，可以用来做画廊。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703180253TWpnEIz8gU4Sj2fJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070318025489sihmGfJP3DZWCM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>这处改建里最值得注意的是墙面的颜色、家具和灯光效果的搭配。有些地方用不同亮度的紫色搭配，让房间的气氛更活泼，适合作为走廊或者会客。有些地方是传统的米白色，配合青色的榻榻米，让空间显得安静而居家。</p>\n<p>灯光的设计来自专门的灯光设计师東海林弘靖（Shoji Hiroyasu），他将不少光源藏在了屋顶里面或是木梁内侧，让光线顺着墙壁呈现出渐变的效果，也呼应整体空间里静谧的气氛。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703180254sJ23q4gdxRzmIkSQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703180255fNDgjoM0d5SyJPla.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703180255QsKHWSVGwYPnt0hr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703180256Y15RzdC4vEMnxghV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703180256LBVqGdlmQKnRozTJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703180257vpUswkeWZ3Dy0qbI.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703180257eJjAa4z1QLth7oP6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>黑色和白色都用在其中调和色调，比如黑色的半透明玻璃门让空间有更多变化，也增加了不少现代气息。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703180258gZazc7qOyn5DbUKs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031802580FS9hZKqa6iuLjYx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>因为委托者喜欢手工艺，事务所请来了当地的手工匠人定做长桌和椅子。茶室窗户的角度开向花园，更加融入自然环境中，从花园向内看，这里也是一幅居家的图画。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703180259UJETvgKxaFqHRQZL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031802597bFihfe6s2ST0VoN.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">图片来自 <a href=\"http://www.wallpaper.com/architecture/case-real-convert-a-japanese-storehouse-into-a-contemporary-work-space#158098\">wallpaper</a>、<a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/architecture/case-real-house-with-a-kura-in-gosho-higashi-kyoto-japan-04-26-2016/\">designboom</a></p>\n\n"}